// text geometry 

:mate Air G4_AIR
:mate Ge  G4_Ge

:p world 400*mm
:p radius 30*mm
:p height 60*mm

:rotm r000 0 0 0

:solid WorldBox BOX $world $world $world
:solid Detector TUBE 0*mm $radius $height

:volu worldVol WorldBox Air
:vis worldVol OFF

:volu detVol Detector Ge
:color detVol blue

:place detVol 0 worldVol r000 0 0 0